  <entry>
    <title>html快速入手</title>
    <link href="/frontend/html/htmlQuickStart/"/>
    <url>/frontend/html/htmlQuickStart/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="HTML知识"><a href="#HTML知识" class="headerlink" title="HTML知识"></a>HTML知识</h2><h3 id="HTML基本框架"><a href="#HTML基本框架" class="headerlink" title="HTML基本框架"></a>HTML基本框架</h3><p>&emsp;&emsp;具体参见下面代码:</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs html"><span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- 声明HTML的版本 --&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-meta">&lt;!DOCTYPE <span class="hljs-meta-keyword">html</span>&gt;</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- HTML的根标签 --&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">html</span>&gt;</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- HEAD 标签</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">    该标签内部主要是关于该网页的信息，有关标签有meta，link，title --&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">head</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- 页面的标题 --&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">title</span>&gt;</span>Hello html!<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">title</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">head</span>&gt;</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- BODY标签</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">    该标签内部主要是用于页面的展示 --&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">body</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">h1</span>&gt;</span>Welcome to Html<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">h1</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">p</span>&gt;</span>I&#x27;m LordBao<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">p</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">p</span>&gt;</span><br>        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Sint recusandae<br>        suscipit iure quia repellat, necessitatibus ipsum placeat alias sequi<br>        cumque temporibus laborum illo, consequuntur ad doloribus asperiores optio<br>        facilis ex?<br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">p</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">body</span>&gt;</span><br><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">html</span>&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><br></p><h3 id="空格"><a href="#空格" class="headerlink" title="空格"></a>空格</h3><p>&emsp;&emsp;通常情况下，在html中，<strong>连续的多个空格只能起到一个空格的作用</strong>。</p><p>考虑一行有着连续空格的代码：</p><p><img src="htmlQuickStart/image-20210703103035312.png" alt="Many Continuous Spaces In Code"></p><p>在浏览器中却呈现为一个空格:</p><p><img src="htmlQuickStart/image-20210703103232968.png" alt="Only One Space In Browser"></p><p>可以采用<code>&amp;emsp;</code>等符号显示声明空格。</p><p><br></p><h3 id="Lorem排版设计"><a href="#Lorem排版设计" class="headerlink" title="Lorem排版设计"></a>Lorem排版设计</h3><p>&emsp;&emsp;Lorem是Emmet工具中的一种特性：可以用<code>lorem</code>来产生大量文字来进行排版设计。可以具体制定产生的字个数，比如<code>lorem10</code>将产生10个文字。</p><p>测试:</p><p><img src="htmlQuickStart/image-20210703103837332.png" alt="Lorem Code"></p><p>效果:</p><p><img src="htmlQuickStart/image-20210703103919392.png" alt="Lorem Effect"></p><p><br></p><h3 id="img图片"><a href="#img图片" class="headerlink" title="img图片"></a>img图片</h3><p>&emsp;&emsp;img标签的作用是引入图片。相关的知识已经放在下面的html代码中了。</p><p>代码：</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs html"><span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- img最重要的src属性，它指明了图片的来源。通常图片来源分为内链和外链，</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">内链即为本网站的图片，用相对路径或绝对路径标识。外链其他网站的图片。 --&gt;</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- 1.绝对路径 以斜杠/开头， 除非项目的根路径不变，那么则采用此方式。</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">可能存在一些根路径不同的情况，比如VSCode预览方式的根路径会以你打开的文件夹为根路径。</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">而Win10的资源管理器则以C盘或D盘为根路径。将你的项目拷贝给别人的话，这种方式常常会导致图片无法呈现。</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">--&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- img 有若干属性 其中src是必选属性，alt是可选属性，但推荐写上，因为当你图片失效时，alt属性会提醒页面的浏览者该图片的相关信息 --&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">img</span> <span class="hljs-attr">src</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;/html/course/html5.png&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">alt</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;html logo&quot;</span> /&gt;</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- 2.相对路径更加灵活得多，图片的具体引入方式是图片相对于当前编辑页面（html)的位置 --&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- height属性是设置图片的高度，这里采用的是绝对大小，当然还可以采用相对大小：即百分比。</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">代表的含义是相对浏览器窗口的大小。与height对应的有width。</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">height和width属性的设置并不会影响真实存在图片的大小。 --&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">img</span> <span class="hljs-attr">src</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;./landscape.jpg&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">alt</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Landscape&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">height</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;200&quot;</span> /&gt;</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- 上面的两种方式都是图片内链的方式，除此外，还有图片外链的方式 --&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">img</span> <span class="hljs-attr">src</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;https://www.bit.ly/fcc-relaxing-ct&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">alt</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;A Lovely Cat&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果：</p><p><img src="htmlQuickStart/image-20210703110352544.png" alt="img Effect"></p><p><br></p><p>考虑<code>&lt;img src=&quot;https://www.bit.ly/fcc-relaxing-cat&quot; alt=&quot;A Lovely Cat&quot;&gt;</code>这行代码失效的情况（比如图片已删除，图片路径错误），那么它就会呈现alt的提示文字。</p><p><img src="htmlQuickStart/image-20210703110552970.png" alt="image Failure"></p><p><br></p><p>常见的图片网站有 Pexels，Pixababy，具体参见 <a href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/299068800" target="_blank">有哪些好用的无版权图片网站？</a> </p><p><br></p><h3 id="a超链接"><a href="#a超链接" class="headerlink" title="a超链接"></a>a超链接</h3><p>通常用a标签指向其他网页，常用的用法有三种。</p><ul><li>指向外网页面</li><li>指向本网其他页面</li><li>页内跳转</li></ul><p>用法1案例：</p><p>·<code>&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.baidu.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;百度首页&lt;/a&gt;</code></p><p>其中href里面写你要跳往的网址，这是必选的，这里链向的是百度的首页面。而target是可选的，常见的设值是<code>_blank</code>,主要是用于新建一个窗口，并在新窗口中跳往href指向的页面。</p><p>用法2案例：</p><p><code>&lt;a href=&quot;002img.html&quot;&gt;002img.html&lt;/a&gt;</code></p><p>这个和用法1没什么区别，就是跳往的页面是本网站的页面而已，采用的方式既可以是相对，也可以是绝对，和IMG图片是类似的。</p><p>用法3案例：</p><p>这种用法常用来跳往页面的某个部分，比如我们常见的TOP，就是用来跳往页面开头的。考虑如下代码:</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs html"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">h1</span> <span class="hljs-attr">id</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;top&quot;</span>&gt;</span>测试超链接<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">h1</span>&gt;</span><br>   <span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- 省略10000行代码 --&gt;</span> <br>   <span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- 内链  页内跳转 --&gt;</span><br>   <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">a</span> <span class="hljs-attr">href</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;#top&quot;</span>&gt;</span> top <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">a</span>&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>其中#top中的top与h1标签中的id属性中的值必须是一样的，那么点击超链接就会跳往h1标签。</p><p><br></p><p>除此以外，超链接还有两种用法也较为常见，</p><p>一种是<code>&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;我哪也不跳&lt;/a&gt;</code>。这种方式超链接哪里也不会跳，常用来测试。</p><p>一种是在超链接中加图片以替换文字，比如：</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs html"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">a</span> <span class="hljs-attr">href</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;https://www.baidu.com/&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">img</span> <span class="hljs-attr">src</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;baidu.png&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">alt</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;baidu logo&quot;</span> /&gt;</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">a</span>&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><br></p><h3 id="sub-sup-em-strong-特殊字符"><a href="#sub-sup-em-strong-特殊字符" class="headerlink" title="sub,sup,em,strong,特殊字符"></a>sub,sup,em,strong,特殊字符</h3><p>&emsp;&emsp;它们是干什么用的？看代码的效果就知道了</p><p>代码:</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs html"><span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- sub  和 sup  --&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">p</span>&gt;</span> H<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">sub</span>&gt;</span>2<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">sub</span>&gt;</span>O , y = a<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">sup</span>&gt;</span>x<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">sup</span>&gt;</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">p</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- strong 和 em --&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">p</span>&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">strong</span>&gt;</span> LordBao <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">strong</span>&gt;</span> once said ，<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">em</span>&gt;</span>有志者事竟成,破釜沉舟,百二秦关终属楚<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">em</span>&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">p</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- 特殊符号 --&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">p</span>&gt;</span><span class="hljs-symbol">&amp;copy;</span>LordBao<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">p</span>&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果:</p><p><img src="htmlQuickStart/image-20210703115325409.png" alt="some tags&#39; effect"></p><p><br></p><h3 id="列表list"><a href="#列表list" class="headerlink" title="列表list"></a>列表list</h3><p>列表分为无序列表和有序列表。其中ol是有序，ul是无序，而li是二者的子元素。</p><p>测试代码如下：</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs html"><span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- 测试list --&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">ol</span>&gt;</span><br>  <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">li</span>&gt;</span><br>    Jack :<br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">ul</span>&gt;</span><br>      <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">li</span>&gt;</span>13<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">li</span>&gt;</span><br>      <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">li</span>&gt;</span>male<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">li</span>&gt;</span><br>      <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">li</span>&gt;</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">a</span> <span class="hljs-attr">href</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;#&quot;</span>&gt;</span>details<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">a</span>&gt;</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">li</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">ul</span>&gt;</span><br>  <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">li</span>&gt;</span><br>  <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">li</span>&gt;</span><br>    Tommy :<br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">ul</span>&gt;</span><br>      <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">li</span>&gt;</span>15<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">li</span>&gt;</span><br>      <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">li</span>&gt;</span>male<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">li</span>&gt;</span><br>      <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">li</span>&gt;</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">a</span> <span class="hljs-attr">href</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;#&quot;</span>&gt;</span>details<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">a</span>&gt;</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">li</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">ul</span>&gt;</span><br>  <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">li</span>&gt;</span><br>  <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">li</span>&gt;</span><br>    Sara :<br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">ul</span>&gt;</span><br>      <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">li</span>&gt;</span>16<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">li</span>&gt;</span><br>      <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">li</span>&gt;</span>female<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">li</span>&gt;</span><br>      <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">li</span>&gt;</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">a</span> <span class="hljs-attr">href</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;#&quot;</span>&gt;</span>details<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">a</span>&gt;</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">li</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">ul</span>&gt;</span><br>  <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">li</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">ol</span>&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果(嵌套列表)</p><p><img src="htmlQuickStart/image-20210703120142033.png" alt="Nested List"></p><p><br></p><h3 id="表格table"><a href="#表格table" class="headerlink" title="表格table"></a>表格table</h3><p>&emsp;&emsp;表格的标签为table，它的子标签为tr，表示一行，tr的子标签有th和td，th和td虽然都是表示一列，但是th的语义是表头，效果是加粗。</p><p>代码:</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs html"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">table</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">tr</span>&gt;</span><br>      <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">th</span>&gt;</span>name<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">th</span>&gt;</span><br>      <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">th</span>&gt;</span>age<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">th</span>&gt;</span><br>      <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">th</span>&gt;</span>score<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">th</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">tr</span>&gt;</span><br>    