an class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br><span class="line">68</span><br><span class="line">69</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs html"><span class="hljs-meta">&lt;!DOCTYPE <span class="hljs-meta-keyword">html</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">html</span> <span class="hljs-attr">lang</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;en&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">head</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">meta</span> <span class="hljs-attr">charset</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;UTF-8&quot;</span> /&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">meta</span> <span class="hljs-attr">http-equiv</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;X-UA-Compatible&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">content</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;IE=edge&quot;</span> /&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">meta</span> <span class="hljs-attr">name</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;viewport&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">content</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0&quot;</span> /&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">title</span>&gt;</span>Document<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">title</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">head</span>&gt;</span><br><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">body</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">h1</span>&gt;</span>Welcome To Register Page<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">h1</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- action表示表单提交的目的地，通常是超链接。 method表示提交的方式，常见的是get和post--&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">form</span> <span class="hljs-attr">action</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;#&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">method</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;GET&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- text 提交文本 name属性用于收取数据value，不过这里不需要了解这么多。</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">        required属性要求该文本text是必填的。与required这种不是KV对的属性还有selected，checked，disabled等  --&gt;</span><br>        username:<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">input</span> <span class="hljs-attr">type</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;text&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">name</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">id</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">required</span> /&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">br</span> /&gt;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- placeholder 占位符 并不会作为实际value 通常起提示作用 --&gt;</span><br>        passsword:<br>        <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">input</span> <span class="hljs-attr">type</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;password&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">name</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">id</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">placeholder</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;字母数字特殊字符&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">required</span> /&gt;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">br</span> /&gt;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- email 相比于text而言，它的格式有限制，输入的文本必须含@ --&gt;</span><br>        email: <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">input</span> <span class="hljs-attr">type</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;email&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">name</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">id</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">value</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;example@example.com&quot;</span> /&gt;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">br</span> /&gt;</span><br>        description: <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">br</span> /&gt;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- 相比于text而言，它的输入框更加大，cols属性表示列数，rows属性表示行数 --&gt;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">textarea</span> <span class="hljs-attr">name</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">id</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">cols</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;30&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">rows</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;10&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br>I&#x27;m from ...<br>I like ...<br>contact me  by ...<br>        <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">textarea</span>&gt;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">br</span> /&gt;</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">br</span>&gt;</span><br><br>        <span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- 性别 --&gt;</span><br>        Your gender：<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">br</span>&gt;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- label 的 for属性的值与其他标签的id的值应该保持一致，</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">        那么当你鼠标点击到label时会同样点击到它对应的其他标签。</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">        这种会提高用户的体验度 --&gt;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">label</span> <span class="hljs-attr">for</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;gender#male&quot;</span>&gt;</span>male :<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">label</span>&gt;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- radio单选框，要求属于同一组的单选框的name务必是一致的，以表明它们同属一组 --&gt;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">input</span> <span class="hljs-attr">type</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;radio&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">name</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;gender&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">id</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;gender#male&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">value</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;m&quot;</span> /&gt;</span><br><br>        <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">label</span> <span class="hljs-attr">for</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;gender#female&quot;</span>&gt;</span>female : <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">label</span>&gt;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">input</span> <span class="hljs-attr">type</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;radio&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">name</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;gender&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">id</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;gender#female&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">value</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;f&quot;</span> /&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">br</span> /&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">br</span>&gt;</span><br><br>        <span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- 熟悉的代码 --&gt;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- checkbox 多选框，要求属于同一组的单选框的name务必是一致的，以表明它们同属一组，</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">        但与radio不同的是 checkbox可以进行多选。 checked表示默认选择，radio也可以采用该属性 --&gt;</span><br>        Your Programming Language：<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">br</span>&gt;</span><br>        java：<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">input</span> <span class="hljs-attr">type</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;checkbox&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">name</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;language&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">id</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">value</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;java&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">checked</span> /&gt;</span><br>        python：<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">input</span> <span class="hljs-attr">type</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;checkbox&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">name</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;language&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">id</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">value</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;python&quot;</span> /&gt;</span><br>        c：<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">input</span> <span class="hljs-attr">type</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;checkbox&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">name</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;language&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">id</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">value</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;c&quot;</span> /&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">br</span> /&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">br</span>&gt;</span><br><br>        <span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- 年龄 --&gt;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- select下拉选框，selected表示默认选中 --&gt;</span><br>        年龄:<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">select</span> <span class="hljs-attr">name</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">id</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br>            <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">option</span> <span class="hljs-attr">value</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;13&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">selected</span>&gt;</span>13<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">option</span>&gt;</span><br>            <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">option</span> <span class="hljs-attr">value</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;14&quot;</span>&gt;</span>14<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">option</span>&gt;</span><br>            <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">option</span> <span class="hljs-attr">value</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;15&quot;</span>&gt;</span>15<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">option</span>&gt;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">select</span>&gt;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">br</span> /&gt;</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">br</span>&gt;</span><br><br>        <span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!--提交分为两种  不过button按钮的作用可不止提交--&gt;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">input</span> <span class="hljs-attr">type</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;submit&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">value</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;commit&quot;</span> /&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">br</span> /&gt;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- &lt;button type=&quot;submit&quot; &gt;  commit&lt;/button&gt; --&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">form</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">body</span>&gt;</span><br><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">html</span>&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果:</p><p><img src="htmlQuickStart/image-20210703151139272.png" alt="form"></p><p><br></p><h2 id="推荐安装插件和TIP"><a href="#推荐安装插件和TIP" class="headerlink" title="推荐安装插件和TIP"></a>推荐安装插件和TIP</h2><h3 id="插件"><a href="#插件" class="headerlink" title="插件"></a>插件</h3><p><strong>插件1.LiveServer</strong></p><p><img src="htmlQuickStart/image-20210703122200290.png" alt="Live Server"></p><p>这款插件的好处是可以将你的本机当做是一台服务器，并且可以对你的代码进行实时渲染。</p><p><img src="htmlQuickStart/image-20210703122602634.png" alt="local host"></p><p>当然，关于怎样实时渲染需要去设置，比如是代码是保存之后再渲染，还是说隔了一段时间以后才渲染。</p><p><img src="htmlQuickStart/image-20210703122809886.png" alt="Save Setting"></p><p>after Delay默认是10秒。</p><p>开启和关闭Live Servr的方式至少有两种：</p><p>方式1：</p><p><img src="htmlQuickStart/image-20210703122947585.png" alt="Live Server Method 1"></p><p>方式2:</p><p><img src="htmlQuickStart/image-20210703123021097.png" alt="Live Server Method 2"></p><p><br></p><p><strong>插件2Prettier - Code formatter</strong></p><p><img src="htmlQuickStart/image-20210703123130173.png" alt="Prettier"></p><p>这个主要是格式化工具，比如你的HTML代码缩进问题，大段连续空格问题等等。</p><p><img src="htmlQuickStart/image-20210703123549604.png" alt="How to use Prettier"></p><p><br></p><p><strong>插件3Bracket Pair Colorizer</strong></p><p><img src="htmlQuickStart/image-20210703123743041.png" alt="Bracket Pair Colorizer"></p><p>保证一对一对的括号以不同颜色的形式出现，提高代码的可读性。</p><p><img src="htmlQuickStart/image-20210703123931222.png" alt="Bracket Pair Colorizer Effect"></p><p><br></p><p><strong>插件4Highlight Matching Tag</strong></p><p><img src="htmlQuickStart/image-20210703124153060.png" alt="Highlight Matching Tag"></p><p>当你点击标签时，会使得成对的标签有效果。</p><p><img src="htmlQuickStart/image-20210703124329634.png" alt="Highlight Matching Tag Effect"></p><p>关于这个的配置在该插件里面有提示，你可以将这些配置复制粘贴到<code>settings.json</code>里面。关于如何个性化配置，建议学了CSS的盒子模型之后再来调，现在采用默认配置即可。</p><p><br></p><p><strong>插件5Indent Rainbow</strong></p><p><img src="htmlQuickStart/image-20210703124703631.png" alt="Indent Rainbow"></p><p>该插件的效果是使得你的缩进有颜色体现，增加代码的可读性。</p><p><img src="htmlQuickStart/image-20210703124817528.png" alt="Indent Rainbow Effect"></p><p><br></p><h3 id="TIP"><a href="#TIP" class="headerlink" title="TIP"></a>TIP</h3><p><strong>1.Word Wrap</strong></p><p>如果代码太长了 。编辑代码的时候会不好看。你要来回左右移动滚动条。解决办法是设置word wrap。</p><p><img src="htmlQuickStart/image-20210703143523671.png" alt="Word Wrap"></p><p><br></p><p><strong>2.Emmet</strong></p><p>VScode内嵌的工具，方便代码书写。</p><p>比如只输入标签名，就能输出一对标签。</p><p><img src="htmlQuickStart/image-20210703143825426.png" alt="Emmet Effect1"></p><p>比如一个感叹号，生成整个html基本框架</p><p><img src="htmlQuickStart/image-20210703144057969.png" alt="Emmet Effect2"></p><p>再比如</p><p><img src="htmlQuickStart/image-20210703144246391.png" alt="Emmet Effect3"></p><p>…….</p><p><br></p><h2 id="参考文章"><a href="#参考文章" class="headerlink" title="参考文章"></a>参考文章</h2><p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mU6anWqZJcc" target="_blank">Learn HTML5 and CSS3 From Scratch - Full Course</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
